long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,es,et,fa,fi,f:
Customize your new tab with the  Wallpapers wallpaper extension and display your favorite game in the background.
Beautify your new tab page with a useful, beautiful and fun theme.
NBA Wallpapers New Tab is here to enhance your new tab experience.

All in one tab.

Click 'ADD TO CHROME' to install the  Wallpapers New Tab extension.

Main Features:
* Choose from among many basketball background images and change them
* Select preferred background change feature from settings menu
* Follow the time, date and day information from the top right

Note: For the best experience, click the "Keep changes" button after installing  Wallpapers New Tab. This will show  Wallpaper Theme on every new tab as intended.

In your image searches, you can use the multiple filter features to find the desired image more quickly. The image search filters include License, File Type, Color, Type, and more, allowing you to conduct detailed image searches.

➤ Background:
 Wallpaper New Tab offers a selection of backgrounds with many games directly in the new tab. Change background images with few clicks from new tab.


For more information about privacy and Eula, visit:
https://wallpapertab.com/privacy-policy/
https://wallpapertab.com/eula/
